{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/MoonPoolCaustics_640x274_003.gif?t=1736776961\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Far beneath an icy ocean, Maritime Operative Daniel awakens alone aboard his submarine. His mission to revive COLONY 1265\u2014an abandoned deep-sea mining and research facility\u2014takes a deadly turn as reactivated systems unveil fragments of its haunting past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/HellDive_Door_001.gif?t=1736776961\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Guided only by VIRGIL, his AI companion, Daniel must navigate seven interconnected facilities scattered across the ocean floor, each step bringing him closer to a chilling truth hidden in the darkness. But some horrors are better left buried - something watches, something waits. Descend into the unknown. Revive the colony. Unearth the truth. And remember - survival is expected.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the depths of the Arctic in this first-person horror game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the deep-sea facilities in your submarine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover the mystery of why the facilities were abandoned in the first place.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources, and interact with the environment to complete your mission.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Avoid dying from drowning, fire, suffocation, and attacks from monsters and unknown lifeforms.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3250020/extras/Beatrice001_small.gif?t=1736776961\" /></p>","achi